    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Short uniform jackets, distinguished by a particular breast panel and cut. First worn by lancers in the First French Republic and used in various countries until World War I.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
